        <h2>INTRODUCTION</h2>
        <p>
            Your privacy is important to <strong>SriCine Cinema</strong>. We recognize that when you choose to share information with us, you trust us to act responsibly. This information helps us enhance your movie-going experience with better services and tailored content. This policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and safeguarding of your data. Please revisit periodically for updates as this policy may change as our services grow.
        </p>

        <h2>THE INFORMATION WE COLLECT</h2>
        <p>When you register or use the <strong>SriCine Cinema</strong> website and services (collectively, the "Service"), we collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, location, gender, phone number, email address, username, and password.</li>
            <li><strong>Activity Information:</strong> Browsing behavior, IP addresses, the browser used, and pages or ads viewed. We may track this information through cookies to provide a better user experience, including automated logins and personalized content.</li>
            <li><strong>Movie Preferences:</strong> Details about movie tickets purchased, theater visits, and feedback provided.</li>
            <li><strong>Other Data:</strong> Messages posted on the platform, survey responses, emails, or other correspondence.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>USAGE OF COLLECTED INFORMATION</h2>
        <p>We use the collected data to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Deliver personalized content and recommendations.</li>
            <li>Notify users about new services, promotions, or offers.</li>
            <li>Improve services based on user behavior and preferences.</li>
            <li>Perform statistical analyses of user activity to guide service enhancements.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>SriCine Cinema</strong> does not sell or rent your personal data to third parties. Aggregated statistical data may be shared with advertisers and partners but will not include personally identifiable information.</p>

        <h2>INFORMATION DISCLOSURE</h2>
        <p>Your information may only be disclosed in the following circumstances:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>When you provide express consent.</li>
            <li>When required for the provision of services.</li>
            <li>To comply with governing laws or legal demands.</li>
            <li>To enhance user experience and value.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>In case of business transitions such as mergers or acquisitions, your data may be transferred to the successor entity.</p>

        <h2>SECURITY</h2>
        <p>
            We implement robust security measures, including firewalls and encryption, to protect your data. However, we recommend users employ antivirus software as an added layer of protection. While we strive to maintain a secure environment, no transmission over the internet is entirely risk-free.
        </p>

